data.name: label1.Text
data.value: Specify the folders to include as well as files and/or folders to exclude. Backup is recursive, so be careful not to include a folder contained within a higher-level included folder, or you could wind up with a backup that takes longer than necessary, duplicate files and/or copy errors. Folders will be backed up in the order you specify; the top folder will be backed up first and the bottom one will be backed up last.
